In this repository i describe JPA 2.1 configuration in Play Framework 2.3 and 2.4 with or without Spring IoC container.
The repository has 4 branches:

-in master branch i use play 2.4 and jpa 2.1
-in play23-jpa branch i play 2.3 and jpa 2.1
-there are also two branches that configure play 2.3 with spring ioc container 4.0, one branch use spring for datasource and another use play for datasource management.